@@.notmc-speech; Don't worry, I'll help her. Everything will be fine. But you should go home and get some rest. @@<br>
@@.mc-thoughts; She leads Brooke behind the church. @@<Br>
<<set $isBrookePossessed to 0>>
<<set $isBrookePossessedCD to 0>>
<br>
